#
# CIFLIST
#    GENERATED BY HIP - make sure the Field1 labels are correct!
#
# All comment lines begin with a "#" character.
#
# The following fields are separated by one or more space
# or tab characters.  The Field1 labels MUST be entered exactly as 
# shown below with the following meanings:
#
#      PLAIN --  image that IS NOT used as a transparent overlay
#      DECAL --  image that IS used as a transparent overlay
#      DATA  --  non-image data such as the Cif Listing file.
#
#
# File format:
#
#       Field0        Field1    Field2
#
#       File1.tga     PLAIN     Comment area - put anything from here
#       File2.tga     DECAL     to the end of the line.
#       File3.ext     DATA
#
#
# All files included in the Cif Tree file must be located in
# the same directory as this listing. At present, all images must be in 16-bit
# uncompressed TGA format.  The transparent color is RGB 0,0,0 or 1,1,1.
#
# Output file: CifTree.dat
#
# Always include a copy of this list file in the tree - handy for quick reference
